The paper discusses improvements in the performance of planners, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus of the paper is on hierarchical planning, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also mentions the need for objective comparison of planners, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG). The use of benchmark problems and challenges for planners is related to robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper discusses the need for a standard description language, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE).
